      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772788754726,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Catalog 写入是一个条目列表形式，每个条目自描述类型（2B field_id）与自身内容",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Catalog 写入是一个条目列表形式，每个条目自描述类型（2B field_id）与自身内容",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0dFQwTGsKqCX1tZstf44x",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3444.2672068278025,
      "y": 736.7901785714284,
      "width": 758.779541015625,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 57256082,
      "version": 207,
      "versionNonce": 1661967240,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772786991182,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  +-----------------------+----------------------------+----------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=100 (2B) | EntryCount u64 (8B)  | CatalogEntryObject[0..N-1]  |\n  +-----------------------+----------------------------+----------------------------------+\n  |←    属性号        →|←     列表元素个数    →|← N 个目录条目（变长写入）→|",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  +-----------------------+----------------------------+----------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=100 (2B) | EntryCount u64 (8B)  | CatalogEntryObject[0..N-1]  |\n  +-----------------------+----------------------------+----------------------------------+\n  |←    属性号        →|←     列表元素个数    →|← N 个目录条目（变长写入）→|",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8XB3e8mEND163MB_0JaZx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3917.4118505014562,
      "y": 867.530163456396,
      "width": 1194.3594970703125,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1211109454,
      "version": 597,
      "versionNonce": 385019896,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772952348124,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "+------------------+----------------------------+-------------------+---------------------------------+\n| Field: 99 (2B) | CatalogType (1~4B)    | Field: 100 (2B) | CreateInfo 负载（变长）   |\n+------------------+----------------------------+-------------------+--------------------------------+\n|← 类型属性号 →|←      枚举值           →|← 负载属性号 →| Schema/Table/View/Sequence/Type/Macro/TableMacro/Index |",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "+------------------+----------------------------+-------------------+---------------------------------+\n| Field: 99 (2B) | CatalogType (1~4B)    | Field: 100 (2B) | CreateInfo 负载（变长）   |\n+------------------+----------------------------+-------------------+--------------------------------+\n|← 类型属性号 →|←      枚举值           →|← 负载属性号 →| Schema/Table/View/Sequence/Type/Macro/TableMacro/Index |",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "H0EO7WgNbbEmVgqkSPH9U",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3668.6899261474628,
      "y": 1083.2421874999995,
      "width": 2540.455810546875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1562223570,
      "version": 475,
      "versionNonce": 1287369464,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772952260210,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Table Entry 中的“表级元数据”（SingleFileTableDataWriter::FinalizeTable）\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n| TableStatistics（变长）| RowGroupCount u64(8B)  | RowGroupPointer[0..M-1]（变长）| 101 (2B) | table_pointer (12B)  | 102 (2B)  | total_rows u64(8B)  |  103 (2B)   | index_pointers 旧版（12B×K，变长）| 104 (2B)  | index_storage_infos 新版（变长×L）  |\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n|←    列统计单元        →|←       行组数量            →|←         行组指针序列            →|←              表指针              →|←            表的总行数             →|     ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Table Entry 中的“表级元数据”（SingleFileTableDataWriter::FinalizeTable）\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n| TableStatistics（变长）| RowGroupCount u64(8B)  | RowGroupPointer[0..M-1]（变长）| 101 (2B) | table_pointer (12B)  | 102 (2B)  | total_rows u64(8B)  |  103 (2B)   | index_pointers 旧版（12B×K，变长）| 104 (2B)  | index_storage_infos 新版（变长×L）  |\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n|←    列统计单元        →|←       行组数量            →|←         行组指针序列            →|←              表指针              →|←            表的总行数             →|     ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "C6Nz7lHPWqeibDmsEQlSQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2756.0516801294107,
      "y": 1132.5198334181528,
      "width": 615,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 111533966,
      "version": 448,
      "versionNonce": 2064502664,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772952372237,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    +================= MetaBlock(root) =================+\n    | Field[100] \"catalog_entries\": List<N>                        |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SCHEMA,  [100] schema=... }           |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE,   [100] table=...                |\n    |   |    // 紧随其后：TableMetadata 单元                      |\n    |   |    Unit TableStatistics                                     |\n    |   |    u64 row_group_count                                    |\n    |   |    Seq RowGroupPointer[...]                                |\n    |   |    [101] table_pointer                                       |\n    |   |    [102] total_rows                                         |\n    |   |    [103] index_pointers (旧) /                             |\n    |   |    [104] index_storage_infos (新)                        |\n    |   |     }                                                            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=VIEW,     [100] view=... }               |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SEQUENCE, [100] sequence=... }      |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TYPE,     [100] type=... }              |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=MACRO,    [100] macro=... }            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE_MACRO,[100] table_macro...}|\n    |   └─ { [99] type=INDEX,    [100] index=...               |\n    |        [101] root_block_pointer (旧版可选) }                |\n    +===================================================+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    +================= MetaBlock(root) =================+\n    | Field[100] \"catalog_entries\": List<N>                        |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SCHEMA,  [100] schema=... }           |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE,   [100] table=...                |\n    |   |    // 紧随其后：TableMetadata 单元                      |\n    |   |    Unit TableStatistics                                     |\n    |   |    u64 row_group_count                                    |\n    |   |    Seq RowGroupPointer[...]                                |\n    |   |    [101] table_pointer                                       |\n    |   |    [102] total_rows                                         |\n    |   |    [103] index_pointers (旧) /                             |\n    |   |    [104] index_storage_infos (新)                        |\n    |   |     }                                                            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=VIEW,     [100] view=... }               |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SEQUENCE, [100] sequence=... }      |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TYPE,     [100] type=... }              |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=MACRO,    [100] macro=... }            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE_MACRO,[100] table_macro...}|\n    |   └─ { [99] type=INDEX,    [100] index=...               |\n    |        [101] root_block_pointer (旧版可选) }                |\n    +===================================================+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VDsG_GLeoB65LlZrH7YVn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4205.297602335619,
      "y": 1249.7851562499995,
      "width": 2617.2158203125,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "XXUvwCa7T66MF2h9R3B4Z"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3cV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 658737102,
      "version": 462,
      "versionNonce": 877074568,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772952260210,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "RowGroupPointer（单独展开 RowGroup::Serialize）\n+-------------+---------------------+-------------+-----------------------+-------------+--------------------------------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------------+--------------+--------------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n| 100 (2B)  | row_start (8B)  | 101 (2B)  | tuple_count (8B)  | 102 (2B)  | data_pointers: Count (8B) + 12B×C |  103 (2B)   | delete_pointers: Count (8B) + 12B×C|  104 (2B)  | has_metadata_blocks(1B) |  105 (2B)    | extra_metadata_blocks: Count (8B)+8B×C  |\n+-------------+---------------------+-------------+-----------------------+-------------+--------------------------------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------------+--------------+--------------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "RowGroupPointer（单独展开 RowGroup::Serialize）\n+-------------+---------------------+-------------+-----------------------+-------------+--------------------------------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------------+--------------+--------------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n| 100 (2B)  | row_start (8B)  | 101 (2B)  | tuple_count (8B)  | 102 (2B)  | data_pointers: Count (8B) + 12B×C |  103 (2B)   | delete_pointers: Count (8B) + 12B×C|  104 (2B)  | has_metadata_blocks(1B) |  105 (2B)    | extra_metadata_blocks: Count (8B)+8B×C  |\n+-------------+---------------------+-------------+-----------------------+-------------+--------------------------------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------------+--------------+--------------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Ty_atiUeK9IHubTgGR35r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4202.980646769214,
      "y": 1364.1080729166665,
      "width": 916.3083902994798,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "XXUvwCa7T66MF2h9R3B4Z"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3d",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 545388050,
      "version": 523,
      "versionNonce": 1773835256,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772952260210,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "struct RowGroupPointer {\n        uint64_t row_start;\n        uint64_t tuple_count;\n        //! The data pointers of the column segments stored in the row group\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> data_pointers;\n        //! Data pointers to the delete information of the row group (if any)\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> deletes_pointers;\n        //! Whether or not we have all metadata blocks defined in the pointer\n        bool has_metadata_blocks = false;\n        //! Metadata blocks of the columns that are not mentioned in \"data_pointers\"\n        //! This is often empty - but can be set for wide columns with a lot of metadata\n        vector<idx_t> extra_metadata_blocks;\n};",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "struct RowGroupPointer {\n        uint64_t row_start;\n        uint64_t tuple_count;\n        //! The data pointers of the column segments stored in the row group\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> data_pointers;\n        //! Data pointers to the delete information of the row group (if any)\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> deletes_pointers;\n        //! Whether or not we have all metadata blocks defined in the pointer\n        bool has_metadata_blocks = false;\n        //! Metadata blocks of the columns that are not mentioned in \"data_pointers\"\n        //! This is often empty - but can be set for wide columns with a lot of metadata\n        vector<idx_t> extra_metadata_blocks;\n};",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "l_6C57QNkB-wMzqGzlYJJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5117.412033081062,
      "y": 600.4999999999998,
      "width": 665.0198364257812,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "R16vYJaSv1K8Td1aCQnBQ"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b41",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1701208846,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 2109639160,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772952281253,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 表级元数据中的旧版索引列表\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n  |  103 (2B) | Count (8B) + Index BlockPointer[0..K-1] |\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n                                          其中每个 BlockPointer（12B）为：\n                                          +------------------+------------------+\n                                          | block_id (8B)  | offset (4B)    |\n                                          +------------------+------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 表级元数据中的旧版索引列表\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n  |  103 (2B) | Count (8B) + Index BlockPointer[0..K-1] |\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n                                          其中每个 BlockPointer（12B）为：\n                                          +------------------+------------------+\n                                          | block_id (8B)  | offset (4B)    |\n                                          +------------------+------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rlATtKulc8jIVFxNq3krI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5117.465744018562,
      "y": 806.9453124999998,
      "width": 1208.519287109375,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "R16vYJaSv1K8Td1aCQnBQ"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
