      "updated": 1772952363491,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. FreeListBlock 逻辑负载（第 1 段）\n  +---------------------+-------------------------+--------------------------+--------------------------------------+\n  | FreeCount (8B)  | FreeBlockId[0..F-1]  | MultiUseCount (8B)  | {BlockId (8B)+RefCnt (4B)}×M |\n  +---------------------+-------------------------+--------------------------+--------------------------------------+\n  |←  可重用块数  →| 每项 8B（block_id_t |←   多引用块项数    →| 每项：块号 + 该块引用计数         |\n\n  FreeListBlock 逻辑负载（第 2 段，MetadataManager 状态）\n  +---------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------+\n  | MetaBlockCount (8B) | {block_id (8B) + free_list_bitmask idx_t(通常 8B)}×B |\n  +---------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------+\n  |元数据管理器持有块数量 | 每块：块号 + 该块中空闲子块位图（64 bit 掩码）          |",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. FreeListBlock 逻辑负载（第 1 段）\n  +---------------------+-------------------------+--------------------------+--------------------------------------+\n  | FreeCount (8B)  | FreeBlockId[0..F-1]  | MultiUseCount (8B)  | {BlockId (8B)+RefCnt (4B)}×M |\n  +---------------------+-------------------------+--------------------------+--------------------------------------+\n  |←  可重用块数  →| 每项 8B（block_id_t |←   多引用块项数    →| 每项：块号 + 该块引用计数         |\n\n  FreeListBlock 逻辑负载（第 2 段，MetadataManager 状态）\n  +---------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------+\n  | MetaBlockCount (8B) | {block_id (8B) + free_list_bitmask idx_t(通常 8B)}×B |\n  +---------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------+\n  |元数据管理器持有块数量 | 每块：块号 + 该块中空闲子块位图（64 bit 掩码）          |",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
