      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "RowGroupPointer（单独展开 RowGroup::Serialize）\n+-------------+---------------------+-------------+-----------------------+-------------+--------------------------------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------------+--------------+--------------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n| 100 (2B)  | row_start (8B)  | 101 (2B)  | tuple_count (8B)  | 102 (2B)  | data_pointers: Count (8B) + 12B×C |  103 (2B)   | delete_pointers: Count (8B) + 12B×C|  104 (2B)  | has_metadata_blocks(1B) |  105 (2B)    | extra_metadata_blocks: Count (8B)+8B×C  |\n+-------------+---------------------+-------------+-----------------------+-------------+--------------------------------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------------+--------------+--------------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "93hKMrMIx1vRQE8rShE0r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -587.5579758526411,
      "y": 1147.0383295533213,
      "width": 916.3083902994798,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "sOveGRbImyaXDPn4ji1W9"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1774655736,
      "version": 625,
      "versionNonce": 746956936,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772963871986,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "struct RowGroupPointer {\n        uint64_t row_start;\n        uint64_t tuple_count;\n        //! The data pointers of the column segments stored in the row group\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> data_pointers;\n        //! Data pointers to the delete information of the row group (if any)\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> deletes_pointers;\n        //! Whether or not we have all metadata blocks defined in the pointer\n        bool has_metadata_blocks = false;\n        //! Metadata blocks of the columns that are not mentioned in \"data_pointers\"\n        //! This is often empty - but can be set for wide columns with a lot of metadata\n        vector<idx_t> extra_metadata_blocks;\n};",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "struct RowGroupPointer {\n        uint64_t row_start;\n        uint64_t tuple_count;\n        //! The data pointers of the column segments stored in the row group\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> data_pointers;\n        //! Data pointers to the delete information of the row group (if any)\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> deletes_pointers;\n        //! Whether or not we have all metadata blocks defined in the pointer\n        bool has_metadata_blocks = false;\n        //! Metadata blocks of the columns that are not mentioned in \"data_pointers\"\n        //! This is often empty - but can be set for wide columns with a lot of metadata\n        vector<idx_t> extra_metadata_blocks;\n};",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9iwkm1o9oLh3EragdjPML",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 69.05256991899682,
      "y": 413.2178809182125,
      "width": 665.0198364257812,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "p9ftGtye2MUBuBYOhoxbu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1987587464,
      "version": 240,
      "versionNonce": 1609421448,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772963866842,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 表级元数据中的旧版索引列表\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n  |  103 (2B) | Count (8B) + Index BlockPointer[0..K-1] |\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n                                          其中每个 BlockPointer（12B）为：\n                                          +------------------+------------------+\n                                          | block_id (8B)  | offset (4B)    |\n                                          +------------------+------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 表级元数据中的旧版索引列表\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n  |  103 (2B) | Count (8B) + Index BlockPointer[0..K-1] |\n  +-------------+-----------------------------------------------------+\n                                          其中每个 BlockPointer（12B）为：\n                                          +------------------+------------------+\n                                          | block_id (8B)  | offset (4B)    |\n                                          +------------------+------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MChIuN_l7oxzJ_a6nkoF2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 69.10628085649682,
      "y": 619.6631934182125,
      "width": 1208.519287109375,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "p9ftGtye2MUBuBYOhoxbu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2032745608,
      "version": 437,
      "versionNonce": 1014266360,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772963866842,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Catalog 的 INDEX 条目（旧版可带根指针）\n+------------+---------------------------------+------------+------------------------------+-------------+-------------------------------------+\n| 99 (2B)  | CatalogType=INDEX(1~4B) | 100 (2B) | CreateIndexInfo（变长）|  101 (2B) | root_block_pointer(12B，可选) |\n+------------+---------------------------------+------------+------------------------------+-------------+-------------------------------------+\n \n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Catalog 的 INDEX 条目（旧版可带根指针）\n+------------+---------------------------------+------------+------------------------------+-------------+-------------------------------------+\n| 99 (2B)  | CatalogType=INDEX(1~4B) | 100 (2B) | CreateIndexInfo（变长）|  101 (2B) | root_block_pointer(12B，可选) |\n+------------+---------------------------------+------------+------------------------------+-------------+-------------------------------------+\n \n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wvr-RXfDIGf2FSy-PuFes",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1312.4545151580562,
      "y": 378.10098631298763,
      "width": 749.598876953125,
      "height": 550,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1088449416,
      "version": 657,
      "versionNonce": 1544274424,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772963847819,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "表级元数据中的新版索引存储信息\n+------------+------------------------------------------------------------+\n| 104 (2B) | Count u64(8B) + IndexStorageInfo[0..L-1]（变长）|\n+------------+------------------------------------------------------------+\n              每个 IndexStorageInfo（示意字段）：\n      +---------------+----------------------------------+-------------------------------+\n      | name（变长）| allocator_infos 列表（变长）| 其它元数据（类型/参数等  |\n      +---------------+----------------------------------+-------------------------------+\n                 allocator_infos 的每项包含：\n                 +------------------------+------------------------------+\n                 | block_pointers 列表 | Count u64(8B) + 12B×M |\n                 +------------------------+------------------------------+\n                                  其中 12B 的 BlockPointer 同旧版定义：\n                            +----------------------+---------------------+\n                            | block_id u64(8B) | offset u32(4B)    |\n                            +----------------------+----------------------+\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "表级元数据中的新版索引存储信息\n+------------+------------------------------------------------------------+\n| 104 (2B) | Count u64(8B) + IndexStorageInfo[0..L-1]（变长）|\n+------------+------------------------------------------------------------+\n              每个 IndexStorageInfo（示意字段）：\n      +---------------+----------------------------------+-------------------------------+\n      | name（变长）| allocator_infos 列表（变长）| 其它元数据（类型/参数等  |\n      +---------------+----------------------------------+-------------------------------+\n                 allocator_infos 的每项包含：\n                 +------------------------+------------------------------+\n                 | block_pointers 列表 | Count u64(8B) + 12B×M |\n                 +------------------------+------------------------------+\n                                  其中 12B 的 BlockPointer 同旧版定义：\n                            +----------------------+---------------------+\n                            | block_id u64(8B) | offset u32(4B)    |\n                            +----------------------+----------------------+\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kibR7aWXVxRkNouTa1Wp3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2790.450631886635,
